Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs32\fad(100,200)}翻譯 十六夜刹那 後期 cunhan 時間 deson OPED 歌詞協力 灰羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五話 死神杜恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜的血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的這雙手將露娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 那時我想要抓住什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:01:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麽都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說 明白的還是會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 在這淒涼之地不必久留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:02:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是絆了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 竟然讓你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我擅自跟來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要朝個方向走出這片地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裡既寬廣又乾涸感覺走不出去的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像機械人的墳場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會想象別人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 那些機械人 哪怕一絲也好有其他人關注著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那黑色的一團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 感覺沒多少氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死 直到這雙手抓住什麼東西為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 努力想要活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:06:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡還會有人關注著 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要抓住什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了誰想要活下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命 還得繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡一直在告訴自己 不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉兹 你也休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越來越搞不懂你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你會是一個沒有内心只會戰鬥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也經常不明白自己 只是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有了他要保護的對象 也許會變得軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保護的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服 歐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺今天做什麼都會很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 想幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐吉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣不會不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 輕風好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘下來的確非常輕鬆 不過呼吸有點難受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你極盡去做你想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的願望只有這一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這雙手想要抓住什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住什麼是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼想要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼要前進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不知道前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姊姊一起保衛露娜的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他的眼神捕獲到 最後只有死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們懼怕著這樣一個最強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神杜恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護露娜的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且比任何人都要愛護露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜的守護著 死神杜恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我竭盡破壞一切的那天 在和我的惡戰中活下來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人 也許現在還想著保護露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡辛 是卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別糾纏我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:13:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是什麼死神 你是我的守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜恩 要活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走露娜大人 我所憎恨的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你們兩個住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 難得能存活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有理由再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又有想要活下去的人聚集過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有自己走向毀滅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣了 杜恩別動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護不了也無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜 你愛著的露娜沒死 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜大人還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 露娜還活在這片土地的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別流淚杜恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不去 為了死去的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 我想要抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手會抓住所追求的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 歐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎所希望的 就是歐吉的願望可以實現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說 有了要保護的人會變得軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了保護的人 會變得溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望和死亡的盡頭 人們所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是愛人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了自身的存在 要保護之人就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 為了所信賴的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


